,{"className":"absolute inset-4 border-4 border-foreground bg-primary/20 z-0"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"absolute inset-0 pixel-card overflow-hidden","children":["$","$Ld",null,{"src":"https://images.pexels.com/photos/2749481/pexels-photo-2749481.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=1260&h=750&dpr=2","alt":"The Evolution of Pixel Art in Modern Web Design","fill":true,"className":"object-cover","style":{"imageRendering":"pixelated"}}]}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"w-full flex justify-center my-8","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"flex items-center space-x-2","children":[[["$","div","0",{"className":"w-2 h-2 bg-black","style":{"boxShadow":"2px 2px 0 0 #ff1493"}}],["$","div","1",{"className":"w-2 h-2 bg-black","style":{"boxShadow":"2px 2px 0 0 #ff1493"}}],["$","div","2",{"className":"w-2 h-2 bg-black","style":{"boxShadow":"2px 2px 0 0 #ff1493"}}]],["$","div",null,{"className":"w-32 h-4 bg-black","style":{"boxShadow":"4px 4px 0 0 #ff1493"}}],[["$","div","0",{"className":"w-2 h-2 bg-black","style":{"boxShadow":"2px 2px 0 0 #ff1493"}}],["$","div","1",{"className":"w-2 h-2 bg-black","style":{"boxShadow":"2px 2px 0 0 #ff1493"}}],["$","div","2",{"className":"w-2 h-2 bg-black","style":{"boxShadow":"2px 2px 0 0 #ff1493"}}]]]}]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"prose prose-lg dark:prose-invert mt-8 space-y-6","children":[["$","p","0",{"className":"text-lg leading-relaxed","children":"\n      Pixel art has come a long way from its origins in early video games. What was once a technical limitation has evolved into a deliberate artistic choice that brings charm and nostalgia to modern web designs."}],["$","p","1",{"className":"text-lg leading-relaxed","children":"      The resurgence of pixel art in contemporary web design isn't just about nostalgia – it's about making a bold statement. In an era of high-resolution displays and photorealistic graphics, pixel art stands out by embracing its digital roots."}],["$","p","2",{"className":"text-lg leading-relaxed","children":"      Modern pixel art in web design often combines retro aesthetics with contemporary design principles. This fusion creates unique experiences that feel both familiar and fresh."}],["$","p","3",{"className":"text-lg leading-relaxed","children":"      Key aspects of modern pixel art in web design:"}],["$","p","4",{"className":"text-lg leading-relaxed","children":"      1. Responsive Scaling\n      2. Color Theory Application\n      3. Animation Integration\n      4. User Interface Enhancement"}],["$","p","5",{"className":"text-lg leading-relaxed","children":"      The future of pixel art in web design looks promising as more designers discover ways to incorporate this style into modern projects.\n    "}]]}]]}]]}]}]}],null],"segment":"__PAGE__?{\"slug\":\"evolution-pixel-art-web-design\"}"},"styles":[]}],"segment":["slug","evolution-pixel-art-web-design","d"]},"styles":[]}],"segment":"blog"},"styles":[]}]}],["$","$Le",null,{}]]}]}]}],null]
